"link:{resteasy-reactive-api}/org/jboss/resteasy/reactive/server/ServerResponseFilter.html[`@ServerResponseFilter`]\n"
"annotation:"
msgstr "同样，响应过滤器也可以使用 link:{resteasy-reactive-api}/org/jboss/resteasy/reactive/server/ServerResponseFilter.html[@ServerResponseFilter] 注解进行声明："

